snippet.title: Introducing Season Zero Warm-Up | Gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
🚀Sharpen your skills to prepare for future earnings.

🕛 Launch date: May 30th at 12:00 PM UTC.

🔥 What's Inside:
· 20,000,000 LRT + $5,000 USDT Leaderboard Airdrop
· Open to everyone, Free to Play
· Earn points by killing aliens and capturing bases to climb the leaderboard
· First 10,000 players get a special Pioneer Badge with future benefits

Remember, Season Zero is the warm-up season, kicking off ongoing weekly updates.

About LandRocker
LandRocker is a P2E game about discovery and space exploration. As a brave and resourceful player, you'll journey to faraway planets, launching exhilarating mining missions to collect rare and valuable resources such as NFTs, crypto tokens, and crafting materials.

Learn more:
Play: https://landrocker.io/start-mining
Website: https://landrocker.io/
Telegram: https://t.me/landrockerchat
Twitter: https://x.com/landrocker_io
Medium: https://landrocker.medium.com/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/landrocker
All links: https://linktr.ee/LandRocker
